title: Audits on Mutant Cats Contracts
body: Smart contracts are constantly tested by malicious parties for vulnerabilities. Upon completion of an audit, reports would be made available for all to see directly on mutantcats.io.  Should we have the smart contracts go through professional audit for the peace of mind of all current and future holders?
author: 0xa11435b21e0Eff08A6c2c5b8316ACC94054e8bAB
